11 March
WHO Situation Report 51:[435]

Albania reported three new cases, taking the country's total to 15. The first death in the country was also reported.[436]
Armenia confirmed three new cases, bringing the total number to 4.[437]
Australia reported 19 new cases, taking the country to a total of 126. American actor Tom Hanks and wife Rita Wilson were diagnosed with the illness during the filming of the Baz Luhrmann's upcoming-biographical film Elvis in Australia.[438]
